&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click on &lt;strong&gt;Open In Operator&lt;/strong&gt; to see the pre-filtered view of the deployed resources in the cluster&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Finish&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
